latestIgtvVideos.title: Kazimacosmetics Product Combo Review
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi guys, I'm receiving an amazing product combo from @kazimacosmetics

1) I tried this really cooling Aloevera Gel by #kazimacosmetics 
This is a Clear Transparent Gel. This is 100% Natural Product. This is good for all types of skin. Be it oily, dry, normal or combination skin. This works best on acne prove skin. You just have to apply it on your face and leave it for 20-30 minutes and wash it off.

2) Secondly Neem and Tulshi shower gel from #kazimacosmetics 
This refreshing shower gel comes in nice cute bottles which seems travel friendly too. This product's fragrance is really osam. Try them for an amazing bathing experience.

3) Thirdly I received this Beard Oil with Moroccan Argan.
How To Use :  Place a small amount of approximately 4-5 drops of Beard Oil in the palm at on hand. Rub your palms together with the Beard Oil. Rub and massage throughly into all areas of your beard.
